er. To improve your traffic, Atomic Mall submits your items to search engines such as Google and Bing. In addition, Atomic Mall has an extensive feedback system that shows comments from your past buyers and other auction sites, as well as a fulfillment rating. The feedback improves consumer confidence and, if your rating is good, your sales.","Atomic Mall lacks several selling features that other online auction sites have. The service does not offer a resolution center for buyer-seller conflicts. Instead, you create your own return and shipping policies, and you are mostly on your own to enforce them. You cannot cancel an auction early or list your items in more than one category. Also, buyers cannot search for items by seller, so your buyers can&#39;t easily stay posted on your new items for sale.","One feature this bidding site does offer to attract buyers is numerous payment options. It accepts money through Amazon Payments, Bitcoin, PayPal, Xcoin, Visa or MasterCard. You can select which payment methods you will accept on each listing.","Atomic Mall&#39;s support options are limited. The service does not have a telephone or live chat option. The only way to talk with a representative is through email. However, you can chat live with potential buyers and sellers. The site has an extensive FAQs page, as well as a community forum that discusses solutions to common user problems."]},"id":"72b16bc4-7f94-431c-96a9-389d8fb58219","type":"text"},{"data":{"text":"Summary"},"id":"bca03507-b984-4173-8b64-55f61c7cf99b","type":"heading"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["Atomic Mall offers a safe marketplace for both buyers and sellers. The service has a rapidly growing user base and tools to help you bring in customers. While it charges several selling fees that cut into your profit, you have good selling potential with this service and all it does to advertise your products."]},"id":"5d4c0a64-58bd-43d8-bc2d-1d9ccfd4beb0","type":"text"}]],"body":null,"legacyId":"product_review_page_62